strings.Value: "Yeah! They know how to feast at the Rushlight Tournament! When's the next one?!"
"Whenever it is, I'm definitely coming with you!"
"Irovetti's entertainments are crude... But still, I must admit, they are not without a certain barbaric charm. When will we attend another holiday in these lands so full of life?"
